<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Account Deactivated - TravelTales</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        padding: 20px;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;
        padding-bottom: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .header h1 {
        color: #2c3e50;
      }
      .content p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .reactivate-btn {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #777;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>TravelTales</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi <strong><%= username %></strong>,</p>

        <p>
          You've successfully deactivated your TravelTales account. Your profile, posts, trips, and other data are now hidden from other users.
        </p>

        <p>
          If this was intentional, no action is needed. Your data remains safe and intact.
        </p>

        <p>
          To reactivate your account in the future, simply <strong>log in again</strong> using your email and password. You’ll be immediately reactivated and can continue sharing your adventures.
        </p>

        <a class="reactivate-btn" href="<%= loginUrl %>">Reactivate via Login</a>

        <p>If you didn’t initiate this deactivation, please contact our support team immediately.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> TravelTales. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
